-->lang : Used fort the java language stuff like operators(primitive) to add/subtract/multiply etc.
It is a In-Built package

--> io package: what it contains means input & output classes
It is used for file reading for optimizing, writing, Buffer Reader etc these go inside io package

--> Util : contains utilities use for data structutres and stuff 
Also collections, frameworks also well

-->Applet: For Development 

-->awt: for GUI(Graphical User Interface)

-->net: we are working with the networking applications
